WEBVTT

00:08:25.703 --> 00:08:30.260
So, almost everybody
is exposed to air pollution.

00:08:31.114 --> 00:08:35.103
Whether you live in a rural area
or an urban area,

00:08:35.127 --> 00:08:39.450
whether you live in a high-income country
or a low-income country,

00:08:39.474 --> 00:08:42.779
everybody's brains, including yours,

00:08:42.803 --> 00:08:44.152
are at risk.

00:08:44.659 --> 00:08:46.379
As a medical doctor,

00:08:46.403 --> 00:08:51.418
I have been dedicating
the last more than 20 years now

00:08:51.442 --> 00:08:53.208
of my professional life

00:08:53.232 --> 00:08:57.343
to raise awareness about
public health issues,

00:08:57.367 --> 00:08:58.804
public health risks,

00:08:58.828 --> 00:09:00.482
at the World Health Organization,